headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Meta Stock Drops After Earnings; Moderna Surges
summary: A social media giant faltered on Thursday, Oct. 30, 2025, as a tax event weighed on its results, while a biotech name benefitted from reports of talks with a major pharma player.

headline: Moderna stock soars after report of potential buyout talks
summary: Investing.com -- Moderna (NASDAQ:MRNA) stock surged as much as 12% Thursday following a STAT News report that the COVID-19 vaccine maker has been in discussions with at least one large pharmaceutical company about "a deal of significant scope," which could include a potential acquisition.
